# We Will use an API.  What is an API ?
=> API Means Aplication Progarming Interface. A software intermediary that allows two applications to talk to each other. APIs are an accessible way to extract and share data within and across organizations.

# A Todo List app 

# Some General Steps To a Follow

- Functionality 
    - Add a Todo
    - Delete a Todo
    - check a Todo
    - Total item count

- Data
	- tasks - an array
	- task - {done, text, id}

- Functions (in code)
	- addTodo
	- deleteTodo
	- checkTodo
	- renderTodosList
	- showNotification (Alert)